# ─── Rust / Cargo ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/target
**/*.rs.bk

# Profiling / coverage artifacts (local-only, never checked in)
*.profraw
*.profdata
/flamegraph.svg
/perf.data
/perf.data.old
tarpaulin-report.*
cobertura.xml

# ─── Sprint-specific ignored directories ──────────────────────────────
# Created by the app at runtime; screenshots, reference exports, and
# benchmark harness output. Per docs/design/sprints/sprint_0_scaffolding.md.
/captures/
/benchmarks/

# ─── Obsidian vault symlink (local editing convenience) ───────────────
# docs/design is a symlink into the author's personal Obsidian vault —
# absolute paths that won't resolve on any other machine. Sprint plans
# and design docs live outside the repo for now. docs/architecture was
# previously symlinked too but is now a real tracked directory.
/docs/design

# ─── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log

# ─── Environment / secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Defensive — none of these should ever be committed. Keep .env.example
# as a template if one is ever added.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
credentials.json
secrets.json

# ─── Claude Code / AI tool per-user overrides ─────────────────────────
# CLAUDE.md is committed (team context); CLAUDE.local.md is per-user
# and must not be shared.
CLAUDE.local.md

# ─── macOS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
._*
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
.fseventsd
.DocumentRevisions-V100
.TemporaryItems
.VolumeIcon.icns

# ─── Editors / IDEs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
.zed/
*.swp
*.swo
*.swn
*~
